title: Electric Organ Music Loops for Casual Games
description: Four electric organ loops with positive vibe and happy mood. Perfect for casual games. Additional intro/end/short variations included!
longDescription:
Soundcloud Preview: soundcloud.com/unreal-music-maketplace/sets/electric-organ-music-loops-for-casual-games-unreal-marketplace-demo

The contains 4 simple yet effective organ "minisongs" loops with positive vibe and happy mood. they will work perfectly in any casual game, platform, child game, puzzle, etc
Each song has minimal melodic elements so it will not annoy the player and will leave plenty of room for sound effects and voiceovers.
The tracks are divided in intro, a looped version (about 1' long), and separate ending clip that can be used to end the song in any moment after level end.
Some of the songs contains also shorter bonus loops/ends that can be used in transitions screens like shops, level intro/end, selections, bonus, etc.
